Get the collections implemented in the package

Source: R/get_collections_available.R
get_collections_available.Rd

Get the collections implemented in the package and a set of related information

get_collections_available()

Value

A data.frame with the available collections, and a set of related information. Main columns are :

  • collection :Collections available through opendapr

  • source :source

  • long_name :Collection long name

  • url_metadata :URL pointing to metadata about the collection

  • doi :DOI of the dataset

  • url_opendapserver :URL of the OPeNDAP server from which the data is extracted

  • status :Implemented status in sopendapr

  • crs :Coordinates reference system of the collection

Examples


(collections <- get_collections_available())
